text: champoh brachachn now krong mea di nah ning puok areab chonobt del now choumvinh puokke min del baohbng anakneasar robsa a l laoh ( pel mean sangkream)laey haey puokke ka min sraleanh khluon robsa puokke cheang roub keat( anakneasar) der . teangnoh ku daoysaarte kar se r k tuk ning kar htnuey ning kar se r k khlean min bangk phl bah peal dl puokke nowknong meakra robsa a l laoh( sangkream) . haey puokke min chheancheung tow tikanleng na del thveu aoy puok brachheang mean kamhoeng laey haeyka min del chuobabrateah pheap krohthnak avei pi satrauv der . phtoytowvinh trauv ban ke kttra samreab puokke nouv ampeula daoysaar brakear teangnih . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh pitchea min bambat phalbony robsa banda anak sang ampeula laey
